<p><img data-action="zoom" class="aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/09/97qF6t0szhEVu21NsNlM.jpg" alt="" width="724" height="956" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">以上图为买家信用体系</p>
<h3>2. 直播互动中粉丝亲密度成长体系</h3>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class="aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/09/0DRtVVFBBarMxFzxskLx.jpg" alt="" width="409" height="1538" /></p>
